THe first dream was that there was a panther in the house trying to get me. THe rooms were set diff. At the end of the hall if you turned left into my brothers room you'd go up a few stairs, turn right. go up a few more and be in his room. My room was on the other side of the hall with the same procedure but going down. I didn't get caught. It was a thrilling dream though.
